### Multi-Tenant SaaS API Examples
### Base URL: https://localhost:5001

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Health Check

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Authentication

### Login and get JWT token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenantId": 1
}

### Projects

### Get all projects for current tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get specific project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Create new project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Project Name"
}

### Create another project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another Project"
}

### Update project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Project Name"
}

### Delete project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Test with different tenant (will get 400 if different tenant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: 2

### Request with correlation ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Correlation-Id: my-custom-correlation-id

### Notes:
### 1. Replace {{token}} with actual JWT token from login endpoint
### 2. Replace {{tenantId}} with your tenant ID (default: 1)
### 3. All endpoints require X-Tenant-Id header or TenantId in JWT
### 4. Responses include X-Correlation-Id header for tracing
